 tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 19, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ars1689059701075.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ars1689059701075.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ars1689059701075.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ars1689059701075\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This option displays various notification messages in the log file, starting from the\n\t\t\t<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var> before the license expiry date.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LOGFILE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">true</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">false</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var> — any value from <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> (license expiration\n\t\t\ttext is never displayed) through to <code class=\"ph codeph\">100</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">True/false</var> — log all/no license notifications in the log file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If omitted or set to a value less than <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, the default value of\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_TRANSCRIPT</code> is used. If LM_TRANSCRIPT is used, that will apply to\n\t\t\tall types of messages. But if not, the default will be current 30 days for all messages\n\t\t\texcept for the maintenance support notifications.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For maintenance support notifications, it will be set as 0, that is it will be off. This\n\t\t\twill cause the maintenance support warnings to not appear by default. They will only\n\t\t\tappear if LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION is set. If set to a value greater than\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">100</code>, the maximum value of <code class=\"ph codeph\">100</code> is used. Any other\n\t\t\tvalue generates an error message and informs the user that the value will be set to the\n\t\t\tdefault value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LOGFILE</code> also accepts On and Off, true and false. On/true defaults to\n\t\t\t30 days, Off/false is the same as 0. If not specified it defaults to what is specified\n\t\t\ton <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_TRANSCRIPT</code>.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4397041\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4397041\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LM_LOGFILE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 19, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This option displays various notification messages in the log file, starting from the NumberOfDays before the license expiry date. LM_LOGFILE = NumberOfDays | true | false NumberOfDays — any value from 0 (license expiration text is never displayed) through to 100 . True/false — log all/no license notifications in the log file. If omitted or set to a value less than 0 , the default value of LM_TRANSCRIPT is used. If LM_TRANSCRIPT is used, that will apply to all types of messages. But if not, the default will be current 30 days for all messages except for the maintenance support notifications. For maintenance support notifications, it will be set as 0, that is it will be off. This will cause the maintenance support warnings to not appear by default. They will only appear if LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION is set. If set to a value greater than 100 , the maximum value of 100 is used. Any other value generates an error message and informs the user that the value will be set to the default value. LM_LOGFILE also accepts On and Off, true and false. On/true defaults to 30 days, Off/false is the same as 0. If not specified it defaults to what is specified on LM_TRANSCRIPT . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}